name: Prophet of Ethereum
description: $PROPHET is the second chapter of $BOOE $BOOE was created and then launched its first chapter called $HOPE (History of Pepe) 1 month after its launch. $HOPE (History of Pepe) is already listed in CoinGecko. $PROPHET is the second and last chapter of $BOOE. $BOOE is creating an ecosystem with three coins that represent the holy Trinity. The three coins will be linked in the future developments of the project.
